{"type": "article", "id": 4020, "title": "Wrapster 两用耳机收纳支架", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-02T08:18:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233253y9hbzKqAx7IG0LTB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款众筹成功的产品，设计师 Matthew Fleming 在众筹平台 Quirky 上线了一款产品，其实就是一款一物两用的耳机收纳器 Wrapster 。未收纳耳机时，Wrapster 可以作为 iPhone 手机支撑架，需要收纳耳机时，只需将耳机线穿过两侧，卷放在中间，就变身成为一款集线器。Wrapster 提供 6 种丰富的配色，定价 1 美元，<a href=\"https://www.quirky.com/shop/31-wrapster-earbud-cord-wrap\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233252tr8RXjHZP2kYAeda.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.278125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233252xnsMqJhmBfzUOkv5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233253hlOkdLsapzCUntm3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}